[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/904] bumped the 
``stdlib-candidate``
 
``nupm``
 version
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/903] removed the multi-line flag from regexes
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/902] recovered non-lemnos themes
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/896] simplified theme usage
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/894] introduced a new std-rfc command 
``str dedent``
 (a.k.a. unindent) to remove common indentation from a multiline string
Okdro 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/895] added Git completions for the restore subcommand
